c%C3%B4ng/poem-fNHkxXTwgzwd5pAxd6jthA">Nam lộ chí Sơn Thuỷ tự ngộ Dao Cù Vũ Hữu Lợi công - 南路至山水寺遇瑤衢武有利公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Huy-Li%E1%BB%85n/author-aojK5yt7X8rTWmkDYWXgEg">Trần Huy Liễn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Thanh-th%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-hMuTjtWDPO1xJMpVMkos3Q">Thanh thạch - 青石</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn-Ho%C3%A0ng-m%C3%B4n-th%E1%BB%8B-lang-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C3%BAc-Pha-h%E1%BA%A1-t%C3%A2n-c%C6%B0-th%C3%A0nh/poem-po1LSOPMKKObvD1FB6YG7g">Thứ vận Hoàng môn thị lang Nguyễn Cúc Pha hạ tân cư thành - 次韻黃門侍郎阮菊坡賀新居成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Tr%C3%A2m-c%C3%BAc/poem-1t_0qqRe4AB9PgmYyYa1yg">Trâm cúc - 簪菊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/Xu%C3%A2n-s%C6%A1-t%E1%BB%A5-tam-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-h%C3%BD-v%E1%BB%8Bnh/poem-wHSlSvvwnN4Tf9VmfaJ-dw">Xuân sơ tụ tam trường hý vịnh - 春初聚三場戲詠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br></div>	</div>
